# Pi Network Testnet A2U (App-to-User) — Full Implementation Prompt

Use this document to replicate a **production-ready Pi Testnet A2U reward system** in any React + Vite + Supabase (or Deno-deployed backend) app.

---

## 1. Goal

Send App-to-User (A2U) Test Pi payments to 10 unique Pioneer wallets so your Pi app qualifies for Mainnet wallet approval.

**Reward flow:**
1. Pioneer opens your app inside **Pi Browser**.
2. Taps **"Claim Test Pi"**.
3. Backend creates a Pi A2U payment → submits to blockchain → completes it.
4. Backend records the unique receiving wallet address.
5. Repeat with 10 different Pi accounts until goal reached.

---

## 2. Tech Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|-------|------|
| Frontend | React 18, Vite, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS |
| Backend | Supabase Edge Function (Deno) |
| Pi SDK | `pi-backend` npm package inside Edge Function |
| Browser | Pi Browser (mandatory for auth + A2U) |

