## 13. Critical Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| `PI_WALLET_PRIVATE_SEED does not match` | Your seed derives a different wallet than the Pi Developer Portal app wallet | Update the secret to the correct seed for the Portal wallet, OR change the Portal wallet to match your current seed |
| `ongoing_payment_found` / recovery loop | Previous claim was interrupted | The code auto-recovers. If it keeps failing, open Pi Browser → Wallet → cancel the pending OpenPay payment, then retry |
| `payment_already_has_linked_txid` | Duplicate submit attempt | The code extracts the existing txid and completes it automatically |
| `already claimed` (409) | This Pi UID already has a `success` row in `pi_a2u_transactions` | Use a different Pi account to claim |
| No `txid` after submit | Pi network delay or testnet congestion | Wait 30s and check `pi.getPayment(paymentId)`; retry if needed |

